latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Thankyou @godrejprofessional for making this happen . 
We’re sincerely amazed by the opportunity you’ve given us . We feel Proud in being the only Salon in Bhavnagar to be rewarded with the Color Festival . 
Being such a renowned company you take great measures of showing gratitude to your local salon owners . 

Special Thanks to @chetan_harsora for his constant encouragement , guidance & support . His forthcoming response , assistance and advice has been very helpful. @h_hetalsuthar for showing immense dedication , expertise and passion .

We had the amazing opportunity to grasp and learn the new techniques , different sectioning patterns and a whole new perspective to work .

We look forward to be working on more bigger projects and achieving new levels of Success in near future . 
I truely appreciate the confidence you showed in us . 

With my Passion , Hardword and your support I’m sure I’ll do wonders ✨
